{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"715","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"上市櫃拚了 5月營收創今年新高","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報 李娟萍<span lang='EN-US'> 2020.06.11</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%BA%94%E6%9C%88%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6.jpg' style='width: 600px; height: 333px;' /></span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>新冠肺炎疫情打亂全球經濟成長步伐，台灣上市櫃公司在逆勢中力爭上游，<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收合計<span lang='EN-US'>2.72</span>兆元，較前一月小幅增加<span lang='EN-US'>1.13</span>％，創今年單月最高數字，但年減<span lang='EN-US'>3.31</span>％，已連續五月年增率負值。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>創新高家數計有恆大、岱宇、璟德、博智、勤凱、熱映、譜瑞<span lang='EN-US'>-KY</span>等<span lang='EN-US'>61</span>家，較前一月創新高<span lang='EN-US'>82</span>家減少。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>從產業別觀察，上市櫃<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收普遍呈現月衰退，僅電子股面板、主機板、<span lang='EN-US'>DRAM</span>銷售及筆電四大類產業，<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收呈現月成長，而<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收呈現年成長的產業別，則有證券、遊戲、營建、主機板、<span lang='EN-US'>DRAM</span>製造、<span lang='EN-US'>IC</span>設計、面板、被動元件等。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>從類股的角度來看，台新投顧副總經理黃文清分析，以累計營收來看，上市公司之中，半導體類股累計前<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收年增超過<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>％，表現亮眼。而上櫃公司之中，則以航運、農業科技類股累計營收年成長超過<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>％，表現相對突出。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>第一金投顧董事長陳奕光指出，值此後新冠肺炎時代，全球將出現補償性復甦，此一現象，已由原物料開始發酵，近期鋼鐵、水泥、塑化等族群，皆見到報價上揚；而航空及觀光等疫情受害股，營收月增率也開始轉為增加，從季增率預估，傳產族群第二季營收及獲利表現，有望優於電子族群。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>陳奕光估計，電子股部分，第二季因華為提前拉貨，有望維持小幅成長，第三季則在蘋果新機拉貨下，將迎來全年營收及獲利高峰。但也須留意，受到華為禁令影響，電子股第三季也有旺季不旺的隱憂，預期電子族群將是小股當家，遊戲、遊戲機有望脫穎而出。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>國泰證期經理蔡明翰認為，歐美疫情趨緩將使全球景氣出現反轉，導致<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收對於產業趨勢參考度偏低，在投資操作上，仍應以企業後續展望為依據。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>筆電族群第二季雖因疫情導致需求大增，但在需求提前之下，第三季容易出現旺季不旺。<span lang='EN-US'>DRAM</span>雖也受筆電需求而激勵，但後續隨手機需求回升，將有望持續拉升業績。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另外，手機族群與非電的原物料族群，雖<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月表現仍相對疲弱，但後續業績將持續由谷底攀升，因此，股價若因<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月營收數字仍呈衰退，而導致拉回時，蔡明翰建議可逢低介入。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ctee.com.tw/news/stock/283837.html</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-06-15","clk_count":"337"}},"__N_SSG":true}